WEBVTT

00:00.631 --> 00:03.673
Monday seems to be everyone's least favorite day of the week.

00:04.032 --> 00:06.319
But at Starbucks, we don't think Mondays are all bad.

00:07.093 --> 00:09.109
We first walked on the moon on a Monday.

00:10.002 --> 00:12.563
The first comic book superhero appeared on a Monday.

00:13.277 --> 00:15.528
Big Ben started bonging on a Monday.

00:16.623 --> 00:18.826
The first public lift arrived on a Monday.

00:19.935 --> 00:21.703
The UK saw its first cinema,...

00:22.130 --> 00:23.646
...weekly weather forecast,...

00:23.751 --> 00:25.395
...performance of Shakespeare's Macbeth...

00:25.779 --> 00:28.557
...and space invaders game all on a Monday.

00:29.372 --> 00:31.773
Around half a million babies are born each Monday.

00:32.137 --> 00:36.997
And every Monday at Starbucks until February the 18th, tall lattes are just one pound fifty.

00:37.519 --> 00:39.582
See, Mondays can be great.

